{"tid":1738773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【極無恥】被羈留時間上限更改為 72 小時","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:51:58.000Z","uid":44742,"like":9,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":53,"remark":"已收到會員反映本主題內容的真實性有待確定，請各位會員留意。","replies":[{"pid":"d0d833f5c88a85206db2af121a6d84c2194c3726","tid":1738773,"uid":44742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"在 進 行 查 問 時 ， 如 當 局 已 根 據 任 何 有 關 遞 解 出 境 的 法 律 申 請 手 令 拘 捕 及 羈 留 你 ， 則 你 由 被 拘 捕 時 起 計 一 般 可 被 羈 留 不 超 過 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">72 小 時</span></strong> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pol/tc/Pol-1128.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpol%2Ftc%2FPol-1128.pdf&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=0a621b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pol/tc/Pol-1128.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8ec600fd699f10f5e665dd0ee5bf69ab84eabcb7","tid":1738773,"uid":44742,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"警權無限大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee77227ceef0106d12a2fe18aea7ef215deff5d","tid":1738773,"uid":224657,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母話改就改得架？"},{"pid":"269967e5cbba63cdbdd3e645aec815105e8825d8","tid":1738773,"uid":24853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"點解可以改"},{"pid":"ca29214944d601db91fabe4c61a6bedd0372cf48","tid":1738773,"uid":44742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60b348aabfc76534f4bdbb7024bd028b1eb76fc","tid":1738773,"uid":55943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"永久羈留吖笨"},{"pid":"28895fbaaa9680c597f0bca0cfccd884b50e24ac","tid":1738773